"{\"uid\": \"thenorthlines.com-paris-transforms-as-2024-olympics-opening-extravaganza-arrives-amidst-citywide-fervor\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"\\\"Paris turn Olympic extravaganza as Games spirit sweeps the city\\\"  As the highly anticipated Olympics 2024 opening ceremony approaches, the iconic city of Paris is immersed in a celebratory mood despite some hiccups along the way.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 230, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1, \"end\": 6, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999993179, \"rank\": 7.467883122502834e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 155, \"end\": 160, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999993179, \"rank\": 7.467883122502834e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With just days to go for the commencement of the biggest sporting spectacle, strict security measures are causing disruptions for locals even as the city transforms into a one giant stadium.\", \"from\": 231, \"to\": 421, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"From the banks of the scenic River Seine to the world-famous landmarks like Eiffel Tower and Notre Dame, the Olympic five rings and colors can be seen draped across every nook and corner filling residents and visitors with a sense of excitement.\", \"from\": 423, \"to\": 668, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 452, \"end\": 463, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"River Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In an unprecedented initiative, the opening ceremony will feature a lavish floating spectacle on the Seine witnessed by thousands lining up its shores.\", \"from\": 669, \"to\": 820, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 770, \"end\": 775, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 0.9999999999924967, \"rank\": 5.899466615792095e-12, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While preparations for such a grand global event are bound to cause inconveniences, many Parisians have voiced concerns over restricted movement, business losses and large-scale annoyances.\", \"from\": 822, \"to\": 1011, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Transport rates hike and intermittent metro closures have added to citizens' woes.\", \"from\": 1012, \"to\": 1094, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"However, with the action set to begin, hopes are high that the Olympic fever will overshadow all problems.\", \"from\": 1095, \"to\": 1201, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"After Tokyo hosted limited capacity events, Paris promises a grand showcase.\", \"from\": 1202, \"to\": 1278, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1208, \"end\": 1213, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9971521757857675, \"rank\": 0.0018106262005316686, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 1246, \"end\": 1251, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999993179, \"rank\": 7.467883122502834e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"From over 10,000 competitors across 200-plus nations to 329 medal events in 32 sports, the scale is sure to be spectacular.\", \"from\": 1280, \"to\": 1403, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Unconventional creative decisions also underscore the French spirit of doing things distinctively.\", \"from\": 1404, \"to\": 1502, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1458, \"end\": 1464, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9506551715404166, \"rank\": 0.05083848577620881, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With athletes now able to perform in front iconic backdrops, Paris looks primed to stage a momentous return of the Summer Games to its fascinating venue and vibe.\", \"from\": 1503, \"to\": 1665, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1564, \"end\": 1569, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999993179, \"rank\": 7.467883122502834e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As the inaugural event looms large, the sweeping stadium that is Paris awaits a celebration for the ages.\", \"from\": 1666, \"to\": 1771, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1731, \"end\": 1736, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999993179, \"rank\": 7.467883122502834e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"thenorthlines.com is a leading digital platform covering and disseminating the news, views and allied information on evolving public policies and responses pertaining to Indian subcontinent and its neighbourhood with a particular focus on the north India region.\", \"from\": 1773, \"to\": 2035, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1943, \"end\": 1962, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_subcontinent\", \"score\": 0.9996456904610014, \"rank\": 0.000292765335608489, \"text\": \"Indian subcontinent